    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Metrarabdotos sergipensis sp. nov. (MNRJ- 358). A, Part of the colony. B, Part of a branch with zooids. C, Ordinary and maternal zooids. D, Secondary orifices and ordinary avicularia. E, Peristome and condyles. F, Special avicularium with mandible. G, Special avicularium without mandible. H, Ovicell. Scalebars: A, 5 mm; B, 1 mm; C, D, 200 µm; E, 50 µm; F, G, H, 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190142/files/figure.png" ;
